== Mentorship and outreach

- *Teaching Assistant & Research Assistant* --- IIST department, Hosei University. Supporting professors in English-language classes: *Project-Based Learning (PBL)* with 4th-year undergraduates, and *卒業研究 (graduation research)* supervision for Master's students.
- Mentor for *15+ undergraduate students at ESATIC* (École Supérieure Africaine des TIC, Côte d'Ivoire); 5 admitted to graduate programs in Japan and abroad.
- Volunteer lecturer at *2 Japanese high schools* on AI and smart energy systems (200+ students reached).
